#4632
Creekside Path~
A narrow path follows the bank of a clear creek through dense undergrowth south of the glade. @@GFlat stepping stones protrude from the water beside clumps of marsh grass.@@N Dragonflies hover over the creek surface and dart between reed stems. The water is cold and clear, running quickly over a shallow gravel bed.
