Old Ranger Post~
A weathered ranger post stands at a fork in the trail, its @@Gwood bleached silver by years of sun@@N. An old habitat map board beside the post shows preserve boundaries and nesting zones. The map is laminated but faded, its colors worn to soft pastels by long exposure to the weather.
