Stepping Stone Crossing~
Smooth rounded stones span a shallow branch of the creek at this designated crossing. @@GWater rushes gently between the gaps, carrying fragments of leaf and pine debris downstream.@@N Reeds sway on the far bank in the current's soft draft. Preserve markers indicate this as a wildlife crossing point as well as a hiking route.
