#4640
Heart of the Preserve~
An ancient grove of cedar and ash forms the spiritual center of the @@GWhispering Forest Preserve@@N. The trees here are enormous, their trunks wider than a cart and their canopy meeting far overhead in a vaulted green ceiling. Roots have heaved the soil into ridges and mounds over centuries of uninterrupted growth. A profound calm and watchfulness settles over every visitor who enters this grove. The preserve warden keeps station here, ready to confront anyone who would threaten the ancient trees.
~
